name: The cake is not a lie
description:
Mmmm, cake. Oh, what’s that? Pardon us for drifting off there for a second. But man, if you ask us, cake is an absolutely vital part of every birthday, if not a vital part of life in general. 

This card is a celebration of that, and we hope that resonates with you too, because we hope this card will prove to be a triumph, a huge success.

name: New Game
description:
Ah, the title screen. That first “hello” from your game to you. That first moment where the whole world is in front of you, rife with possibility. Get this card for a friend or family member who is encountering a title screen in their life, a moment when they are staring their future straight in the face. Because life is just like a video game, right? 

At least we’re still trying to convince ourselves it is (we’d probably be a lot better at it, if that was the case).
